 European princely families. It was out of favour in England for centuries, however, and the revival of its popularity in the 19th century was largely in honour of  Queen Victoria's  consort,  Prince Albert of Saxe-Coburg-Gotha ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Gruffydd ap Gwenwynwyn was born in 1300, in Wales, United Kingdom as the son of Gwenwynwyn ap Goronwy. He married Alis Ferch Sulien x. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1300–":"1300–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1151–Female":"1151–Surnud","1267–Female":"1267–Surnud","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","1225":"1225","1300":"1300","1267":"1267","1275":"1275","1151":"1151","Wales":"Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1300–":"1300–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1151–Female":"1151–Kuollut","1267–Female":"1267–Kuollut","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","1225":"1225","1300":"1300","1267":"1267","1275":"1275","1151":"1151","Wales":"Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1300–":"1300–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1151–Female":"1151–Décédée","1267–Female":"1267–Décédée","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","1225":"1225","1300":"1300","1267":"1267","1275":"1275","1151":"1151","Wales":"Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Gruffydd ap Gwenwynwyn est né en 1300, à Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni, fils de Gwenwynwyn ap Goronwy. Il a épousé Alis Ferch Sulien x. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1300–":"1300–Verstorben","1300–Male":"1300–Verstorben","1225–Female":"1225–Verstorben","1151–Female":"1151–Verstorben","1267–Female":"1267–Verstorben","1275–Male":"1275–Verstorben","1225":"1225","1300":"1300","1267":"1267","1275":"1275","1151":"1151","Wales":"Wales, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Gruffydd ap Gwenwynwyn wurde 1300 in Wales, United Kingdom, als Sohn von Gwenwynwyn ap Goronwy geboren. Er hat Alis Ferch Sulien x geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1300–":"1300–Desede","1300–Male":"1300–Desede","1225–Female":"1225–Dese